<section>
	<h2>Example: Embedded Search Timeline</h2>
	<strong>An embedded search timeline requires a twitter account to generate the query and widget id.</strong>

	<div class="wb-twitter">
		<a class="twitter-timeline" href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23boew" data-widget-id="329071414877495297">Tweets concernant "#boew"</a>
	</div>

	<section>
		<h3>Code</h3>
